Method Detail

init

public void init()
Description copied from class: ATVapplet
Initializes the Applet. Loads the Tree from value tagged by "url_of_tree_to_load". Opens a Frame (ATVappletFrame) containing the display of the Tree and all the controls. There is no need to call this method, since it gets called automatically whenever a ATVapplet is created. This is part of the atv_awt package. It requires at least JDK 1.1 (but no Swing -- since it only relies on the AWT).
